## 4. Page Transitions

```
Page Exit:   opacity 1→0, translateY 0→-10px  (200ms)
Page Enter:  opacity 0→1, translateY 10px→0   (300ms, 100ms delay)
```

Framer Motion `AnimatePresence`, Navigation bleibt statisch.

